+/*!
+ * ioctl_g_parm - V4L2 sensor interface handler for VIDIOC_G_PARM ioctl
+ * @s: pointer to standard V4L2 device structure
+ * @a: pointer to standard V4L2 VIDIOC_G_PARM ioctl structure
+ *
