+ *                         if \a mode = ADC_1CHAN_8X, the result is \n
+ *                             result[0] = BATTP \n
+ *                             result[1] = BATT_I \n
+ *                             result[2] = BATTP \n
+ *                             result[3] = BATT_I \n
+ *                             result[4] = BATTP \n
+ *                             result[5] = BATT_I \n
+ *                             result[6] = BATTP \n
+ *                             result[7] = BATT_I
+ *
+ * @return       This function returns PMIC_SUCCESS if successful.
